    "These empirical results demonstrate that our TSD metric more closely aligns with human judgment concerning the topic diversity evaluation.",
    "Compared to OCTIS, TopMost covers a wider range of topic modeling scenarios and more newest released NTMs.",
    "It also decouples the model implementations and training, which eases the extension of new models.",
    "These toolkits provide a solid foundation for beginners to explore various topic models and empower users to apply diverse topic models in their applications.",
